==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: bīng lái jiàng dăng, shuĭ lái tŭ yăn
===Etymology===
Literally: (If enemy) soldiers come, a general (should) stop them.  (If flood) waters come, the earth (should) stem it.
===Proverb===
'''[[兵]][[來]][[將]][[擋]]，[[水]][[來]][[土]][[掩]]'''
# Take such measures as the situation calls for.
===Alternative forms===
[[兵来将挡，水来土掩]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])
